*The worker is who is encharge of take the data once an hour from the api and uploaded to mongod
*No ORM needed

1) To request information by title, author or tags, the following route must be followed, keys for search (title, author, tags)
http://localhost:3000/data/
For example:
http://localhost:3000/data/?author=Banana699
or
http://localhost:3000/data/?author=the21st&title=Automatic profiling of Node.js blocked event loop in production
or
http://localhost:3000/data/?tags=story_30582221

2) To delete an item, by the following path and using the _id
http://localhost:3000/item/:id
For example:
http://localhost:3000/item/6226809e8992e7c43054185e

enjoy!
